Gg_devdropdown
===========
The main point of this map was to create a very fast paced gun game.
Without the lag, maximizing fps and not destroying the fun of the game.
===========
Features a wall that separates the map forcing players to drop down to confront the opposing team. Stairs allow access from below, while 2 super-boosters allow you to fly across the map to immediately access the enemies spawn, at the risk of being killed by a spinning hoop.
===========
30spawns. Fast pace. Brought to you by gun game nuts.
